{"tid":1182902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六四領袖封從德在香港機場被帶走 下落不明","createTime":"2019-06-02T13:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T15:38:55.000Z","uid":41695,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"89b41d6a3d11cdc4b11aafee284435fd3ac8b616","tid":1182902,"uid":41695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"港媒報導，「六四」事件學運領袖封從德今天中午飛抵香港機場，在排隊通關時被入境處人員帶走，至今下落不明。封從德原計劃6月4日晚間，參加在香港維多利亞公園舉辦的「六四」紀念晚會。<br />\n<br />\n綜合香港蘋果日報、明報及立場新聞報導，香港入境處面對媒體的查證，到發稿為止尚未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n香港支聯會副主席蔡耀昌則向無線新聞證實，封從德今天上午從東京登機，在下午1時抵達香港，但在排隊入境通關時遭到阻撓，「現被邀請去一個房間」。<br />\n<br />\n封從德在「六四」事件中，是被中共官方通緝的21名學生領袖之一，事後流亡海外。30年來，封從德曾出版多本「六四」相關書籍，建立「六四檔案」網站，透過網路傳播六四真相。<br />\n<br />\n目前，封從德還主持「孫文學校」和「天安門民主大學」兩個網站，傳播民主理念。他曾表示，這是持續與中共政權進行一場「記憶戰爭」。<br />\n<br />\n今年5月18至19日，封從德曾來台參加華人民主書院主辦的「六四事件30週年」大型研討會，並發表演講。當時他說，中共正主導一場「記憶戰爭」，透過結構性暴力影響世人對「六四」的記憶。至於當年「六四」之所以失敗，是學生從未想過推翻中共。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3848718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3848718&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=8a698181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3848718</a>"},{"pid":"ac709bba6d26ffbd683ffadf665fd7899dc19260","tid":1182902,"uid":60049,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe885dad849f3243f79c536dd664988fb6038907","tid":1182902,"uid":41695,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:54:11.000Z","msg":"港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fece35ad73cf78030e3ee97ab085cf09040d563","tid":1182902,"uid":63154,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"原地遣返都唔做，捉埋人上去，呢排外國勢力望到咁實，希望佢嘅壯烈犧牲可以換來西方制裁香港"},{"pid":"7641aada96d2cdc3088e511e397bb6df099d391a","tid":1182902,"uid":57269,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"有活生生嘅例子激起衝突啦<br />\n反送中有位入啦"},{"pid":"ce6cbf220265d42351906a1d377c2a9abdd4adf1","tid":1182902,"uid":550,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"遣返咗日本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566577f01dc817d23bd14bb0b96b998fe1a8b113","tid":1182902,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190602/s00001/1559462954634/%E3%80%90%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B30%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E5%B0%81%E5%BE%9E%E5%BE%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%94%AF%E6%81%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A-%E5%BF%83%E8%99%9B%E5%88%B0%E6%A5%B5%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190602%2Fs00001%2F1559462954634%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B30%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E9%2581%25A3%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%25BE%25B7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2594%25AF%25E6%2581%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258A-%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2599%259B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%25BB%259E&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=0f9ffcc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190602%2Fs00001%2F1559462954634%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B30%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E9%2581%25A3%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E